# This is a documentation repository. Its content is Markdown specifications
# (the White Paper, Yellow Paper, and YPX extensions) — which GitHub's Linguist
# does not count as a "language." The only code-shaped files are the latex/
# build templates, which are tooling, not the repository's subject. Exclude them
# from language statistics so the repo isn't mislabeled as a TeX/Makefile project.
latex/** linguist-documentation
*.tex linguist-documentation
*.cls linguist-documentation
